text: Vultures 1 (stylized in all caps) is the debut studio album from the reborn duo of Kanye West and Ty Dolla Sign, otherwise known as ¥$. It is the first album of a three-volume series, announced with a trailer on January 24, 2024. == Track listing == === Track notes === * "Carnival" features additional vocals from Curva Nord Milano ultras. * "Good (Don't Die)" features additional vocals from J.
